----------------------------
Configuring a server switch
----------------------------
- vtp domain <DOMAIN NAME> :: Configure VTP's Domain
- vtp version 2
- vtp mode server
- vtp password <PWD> :: Password Configuration.

----------------------
Configuring the Client
----------------------
- vtp mode client
- vtp domain <DOMAIN NAME>
- conf term
- vtp mode server :: First switch to server mode to change the version.
- vtp version 2
- vtp password <PWD>
- vtp status


